@startuml
title LowCortisol - Support Backend Class Diagram

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false

package "Not implemented in backend" {
  class "Support backend context" as SupportCandidate
}

package "Frontend module" {
  class SupportTicket
  class SupportMessage
  class SupportAgent
  class KnowledgeArticle
}

SupportTicket "1" o-- "*" SupportMessage
SupportTicket --> SupportAgent
SupportCandidate ..> SupportTicket : future backend candidate

note bottom of SupportCandidate
  The current platform backend does not contain
  a Support bounded context. Support is implemented
  in the frontend/product scope.
end note

@enduml
